# Supabase — Bessa's Box (Vite / Vercel)

## Variáveis na Vercel e no `.env` local

### Cliente (prefixo VITE_ — obrigatório no browser)

```env
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://seu-projeto.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sua_chave_anon_ou_publishable
```

### Servidor (sem VITE_)

```env
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...
ADMIN_EMAILS=seu@email.com
PAYMENT_PROVIDER=mercadopago
MERCADOPAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN=
MERCADOPAGO_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
ASAAS_API_KEY=
ASAAS_WEBHOOK_TOKEN=
```

Guia admin: [`docs/ADMIN.md`](docs/ADMIN.md) | Setup Supabase: [`docs/SUPABASE_SETUP.md`](docs/SUPABASE_SETUP.md)
